    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/59a21ca3ab30ff3126727b1f4bb3d556.poster.avif?t=1771949580\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/59a21ca3ab30ff3126727b1f4bb3d556.webm?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/59a21ca3ab30ff3126727b1f4bb3d556.mp4?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>在这个<strong>惬意的单人采矿探险</strong>中，您要探索神秘的洞穴，寻找古代宝藏和文物。将发掘出来的战利品安全带回地面，卖给当地商人，或在铁匠铺用宝石锤升级和强化自己的装备。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> 不过请放心，要揭开这座岛屿埋藏已久的秘密，克服来自地下的神秘威胁，您将需要一切可能的帮助！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/3954accc0478cd422ca854f3f8e690b7.poster.avif?t=1771949580\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/3954accc0478cd422ca854f3f8e690b7.webm?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/3954accc0478cd422ca854f3f8e690b7.mp4?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>挖掘宝藏</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采矿时要讲究策略。小心使用锤子，挖掘出隐藏在不同硬度岩石层下的宝藏和工艺品。但要注意，每敲击一次锤子，墙壁就会失去稳定性，离倒塌越来越近！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/da06d21453b45dd71ef9d3f79885911e.poster.avif?t=1771949580\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/da06d21453b45dd71ef9d3f79885911e.webm?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/da06d21453b45dd71ef9d3f79885911e.mp4?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>寻找传奇锤子</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的<strong>锤子</strong>是游戏中不可或缺的一部分。一开始，您只能用您最信任的镐来保护自己，随着您的进步，您可以解锁具有特殊能力的新锤子，以便穿越地下！您还需要这些锤子在 <strong> 采矿迷你游戏</strong> 中挖掘宝藏。因此，请明智地选择您要携带的锤子。 <br>如果幸运的话，您甚至可能在旅途中找到传说中的锤子...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/ace3c4d835ca6f7358360822c02a64e7.poster.avif?t=1771949580\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/ace3c4d835ca6f7358360822c02a64e7.webm?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/ace3c4d835ca6f7358360822c02a64e7.mp4?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>探索按程序生成的洞穴</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入神秘的洞穴，发现 8 个独特的洞穴生物群落，每个群落都有自己的噱头和转折。越往深处，越有宝藏和危险等着你。每走 10 层，您就会遇到具有挑战性的老板或令人费解的障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在迷人的采矿迷你游戏中挖掘无数宝藏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的锤子并用宝石强化它们</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索具有独特噱头、敌人和战利品的 8 个洞穴生物群落</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与敌人搏斗，打一场引人入胜的 Boss 战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可扩展背包，采用磁贴式库存设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 为村民完成任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 解开谜题，揭开岛上的传说</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以抚摸 Shadow（狗）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/1cc34bb46e59b1f72d755f0f7b1ec89b.poster.avif?t=1771949580\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/1cc34bb46e59b1f72d755f0f7b1ec89b.webm?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122600/extras/1cc34bb46e59b1f72d755f0f7b1ec89b.mp4?t=1771949580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
